<!-- Policies Content Section -->
<section class="policies-content">
  <div class="policies-container">
    <div class="policies-list">
      <h1>Rental Policies â€“ VoyagerAI</h1>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Age Requirements</h2>
        <p>All renters must be at least <strong>19 years of age</strong> with a valid driver's license. Drivers under 25 may be subject to additional fees and restrictions.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Reservation & Cancellation</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Reservations can be made up to 6 months in advance</li>
          <li>Full refund if canceled 24 hours or more before pickup time</li>
          <li>50% refund if canceled between 2-24 hours before pickup</li>
          <li>No refund for cancellations less than 2 hours before pickup</li>
          <li>No-show reservations will be charged the full rental amount</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Insurance Options</h2>
        <p>We offer comprehensive insurance coverage to protect you during your rental:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Basic Coverage ($10/day):</strong> Covers damage to the rental vehicle up to $1,000</li>
          <li><strong>Standard Coverage ($20/day):</strong> Covers damage to the rental vehicle up to $5,000</li>
          <li><strong>Premium Coverage ($30/day):</strong> Covers damage to the rental vehicle up to $25,000</li>
          <li><strong>No Insurance:</strong> You are responsible for all damages to the rental vehicle</li>
        </ul>
        <p><em>Note: Personal auto insurance may provide additional coverage. Please check with your insurance provider.</em></p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Fuel Policy</h2>
        <p>All vehicles must be returned with a <strong>full tank of fuel</strong>. Failure to do so will result in a refueling charge of $25 plus the cost of fuel.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Fuel level will be documented at pickup and return</li>
          <li>Refueling charges are non-negotiable</li>
          <li>We recommend refueling within 10 miles of our location</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Return Policy</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Vehicles must be returned on time to avoid late fees</li>
          <li>Late return fees: $10 per hour (first 2 hours), $25 per hour thereafter</li>
          <li>Maximum late fee: $100 per day</li>
          <li>Early returns may be eligible for partial refunds</li>
          <li>All vehicles are inspected upon return</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Vehicle Condition</h2>
        <p>Renters are responsible for maintaining the vehicle in good condition:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>No smoking in any vehicles</li>
          <li>Pets must be in appropriate carriers</li>
          <li>Excessive cleaning fees may apply for heavily soiled vehicles</li>
          <li>Report any mechanical issues immediately</li>
          <li>Do not exceed the vehicle's passenger or cargo capacity</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Additional Fees</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Additional driver fee: $15 per day</li>
          <li>Underage driver fee (19-24): $25 per day</li>
          <li>One-way rental fee: $50</li>
          <li>After-hours pickup/drop-off: $35</li>
          <li>Traffic violation processing: $25</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Prohibited Activities</h2>
        <p>The following activities are strictly prohibited and may result in immediate termination of the rental agreement:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Off-road driving</li>
          <li>Racing or reckless driving</li>
          <li>Transporting illegal substances</li>
          <li>Using the vehicle for commercial purposes without permission</li>
          <li>Allowing unauthorized drivers to operate the vehicle</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Contact Information</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about our policies or need assistance during your rental:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>24/7 Support:</strong> 1-800-VOYAGER</li>
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> support@voyagerai.com</li>
          <li><strong>Emergency Roadside:</strong> 1-800-VOYAGER-HELP</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

